data.text:
🎞 🛋 🍿 WikiFlix - Watch free movies 🍿 🛋 🎞

WikiFlix is a prototype for browsing and watching full-length, public domain or Creative Commons-licensed films on Wikimedia Commons. The lists of films on WikiFlix are powered by Wikidata. Not to be confused with WikiFlix (i).

By decade: 1870s, 1880s, 1890s, 1900s, 1910s, 1920s, 1930s, 1940s, 1950s, 1960s, 1970s, 1980s, 1990s, 2000s, 2010s, 2020s

Genres: Abstract films, Animated films, Anime, Science fiction films

Countries: 🇧🇪 Belgium - 🇫🇷 France - 🇮🇳 India - 🇯🇵 Japan - 🇬🇧 United Kingdom - 🇺🇸 United States

Directed by: Walt Disney 📽 Sergei Eisenstein

With actors: Charlie Chaplin

🌟 And a few special lists: 🌟 Films by female directors 🌟 Films by directors who identify/ied as LGBT+ 🇺🇸 National Film Registry

Spinster's thoughts and ruminations behind WikiFlix

This list is periodically updated by a bot. Manual changes to the list will be removed on the next update!
